<p>It is believed that <a href= 
"http://www.cs.jhu.edu/~callahan/lifepage.html"><b>B3/S23</b>
(Conway's Life)</a> and <a href="../b35s236/"><b>B35/S236</b></a>
also support replicators due to <a href=
"../b35s236/construct.html">construction universality</a>, but
explicit replicators for those rules have not been constructed.</p>

